COVID-19 Status 💉 🦠

As of 8:30PM PT yesterday, over 1.3 million Canadians have tested positive for COVID-19. Sadly, 17.8 thousand have died.

In the last day, -1 new infections were reported and 7 deaths. Currently 876 are in the hospital and 20 are in the ICU. This is trending upwards.

Fortunately, 23.4 million doses of the vaccine have been administered. For those 5 years and older, 31.3% have their 1st shot and 19.7% are fully vaccinated!

Vaccination is slowing down, but there are -345 thousand doses in the freezer. It currently takes ~41 days for new deliveries to get into arms.

At the current rate, Canadians should achieve herd immunity around when 80% of the entire population is fully vaccinated. There is no approved vaccine for children under 5.
